section.section:
"Professional service" includes, but is not limited to, a service provided by:
An architect;
An attorney;
A certified public accountant;
A chiropractor;
A dentist;
An osteopath;
A podiatrist;
A physician;
A professional engineer;
A licensed real estate broker, licensed real estate salesperson, and licensed associate real estate broker;
A veterinarian;
A psychologist; and
A physical therapist.
